<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <title>My First Website</title>
    <style>

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        
        .profile-pic {
            width: 200px; 
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover; 
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        
        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #337ab7;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #23527c;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <img src="me.jpg" alt="John Kenneth Gonzales" class="profile-pic">

    <h1>John Kenneth Gonzales</h1>
    
    <h3>BSIT 2nd Year Level</h3>

    <p>
        Hi, my name is Kenneth Gonzales, you can call me Ken for short. 
        My hometown is in Quezon City but right now I'm currently residing here in Sampaloc, Manila. 
        I'm renting a small room around this area. My hobbies were mostly playing video games. 
        I also sometimes do some physical activity like running, playing basketball and table tennis.
    </p>

    <p>
        I took BSIT as my undergrad degree because I want to dwell into the tech industry, 
        specifically in either cybersecurity or as a data analyst. Another reason is that 
        I want to leverage my current experience as a working student and combine it with 
        my degree to level up my lifestyle in general.
    </p>

    <p>
        Check out my work here: <a href="https://github.com/SoulPictor/websys-week1-gonzales-kenneth" target="_blank">My GitHub Repository <i class="fab fa-github"></i></a>
    </p>

    <footer>
        <p><i>"You can be the sweetest peach on the tree, but some people just don't like peaches."</i></p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
